  "section": "1.3: Unlocking bird runs",
  "stepText": "Use your ring of dueling to teleport to Al-Kharid, speak with the gem trader and Avan for Family Crest, mine iron ore in the Al-kharid mine for the diary, give the items for Prince Ali Rescue to Osman. Do a lap of the agility course, rebank to grab quest items, then run south and fish some anchovies south of the bank for the diary, then start The Shadow of the Storm until you have the sigil mould and tome (take the carpet to Uzer the first time for a diary step) using your necklace of passage when convenient.\n",
